    <h1 class="about-heading">"Vegan Dessert"</h1>
    <p class="about-paragraph">When I first went vegan I quickly found out how unappealing the "non-dairy" desserts were. They tasted dry, heavy, and dense (but not in a good way). For vegan desserts they really tasted <i>vegan</i>.</p>
    <p class="about-paragraph">But all of the good stuff was laden with dairy and eggs. After I couldn't find what I was looking for I decided to make it myself. And after being vegan for 11 years I have to give credit to the desserts I was baking (they made being vegan taste great).</p>
