    <div class="about-founder-text-container">
        <p class="about-founder-text">For a girl like me with the world's biggest sweet tooth, this just wouldn't do. I had to take matters into my own hands. So I started baking — and baking and baking!</p>
        <p class="about-founder-text">I baked till my oven pleaded for mercy and over fed my friends, co-workers, and boyfriend until he said "Heather, there are too many desserts in this house so please get rid of them — maybe even sell them."</p>
        <p class="about-founder-text">And that's what I did!</p>
