    <h1 class="about-heading">Small Beginnings</h1>
    <p class="about-paragraph">In 2014 I bought a table at a local vegan market, came up with a name based off of my favorite Misfits song, and baked a ton of treats. I really didn't know what I was exactly doing at the time but I was having a lot of fun baking and hanging out with friends so I kept at it.</p>
    <p class="about-paragraph">For six years I've been hopping from one shared kitchen to another racing to bake as much as I could bring to these pop-ups and local markets — it really was a blast even without a proper shop.</p>
